name: zero
definition: The integer zero (0).

name: one
definition: The default numeral for one (1). // It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.

name: two
definition: The natural number two (2). // It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.

name: three
definition: The natural number three (3). // It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.

name: four
definition: The default numeral for four (4). It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.

name: five
definition: The default numeral for five (5). It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.

name: six
definition: The natural number six (6). // It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.
burmese: ခြောက်ခဲ့သည်

name: seven
definition: The natural number seven (7). // It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.

name: eight
definition: The natural number eight (8). // It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.

name: nine
definition: The default numeral for nine (9). It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.

name: ten
definition: The default numeral for ten (10). It should not include a numeral classifier, but instead be only the bare numeral.

name: eleven
definition: The natural number eleven (11).

name: twelve
definition: The natural number twelve (12).

name: thirteen
definition: The natural number thirteen (13).

name: fourteen
definition: The natural number fourteen (14).

name: fifteen
definition: The natural number fifteen (15).

name: sixteen
definition: The natural number sixteen (16).

name: seventeen
definition: The natural number seventeen (17).

name: eighteen
definition: The natural number eighteen (18).

name: nineteen
definition: The natural number nineteen (19).

name: twenty
definition: The natural number twenty (20).

name: thirty
definition: The natural number thirty (30).

name: forty
definition: The natural number forty (40).

name: fifty
definition: The natural number fifty (50).

name: hundred
definition: The natural number one hundred (100).

name: two hundred
definition: The natural number two hundred (200).

name: three hundred
definition: The natural number three hundred (300). // This is included in the concept list to determine composition of higher numbers.

name: four hundred
definition: The natural number four hundred (400). // This is included in the concept list to determine composition of higher numbers.

name: five hundred
definition: The natural number five hundred (500). // This is included in the concept list to determine composition of higher numbers.

name: 1 du
definition: The speaker and exactly one other person. // The first person dual pronominal stem. In varieties which have this stem, it is typically derived from a proposed etymon #tsi. Varieties which lack stem suppletion for dual pronominal forms should have their compounds recorded as such.

name: 1 du excl
definition: Exclusive form of the dual pronominal stem. This should only be filled out for languages which have a suppletive clusivity distinction.

name: 1 du incl
definition: Inclusive form of the dual pronominal stem. This should only be filled out for languages which have a suppletive clusivity distinction.

name: 1 n sg excl
definition: Exclusive form of the non-singular and non-dual pronominal stem. This should only be filled out for languages which have a suppletive clusivity distinction.
burmese: ကျွန်တစ်ဦးတည်းနှင့်တကွ

name: 1 n sg incl
definition: Inclusive form of the non-singular and non-dual pronominal stem. This should only be filled out for languages which have a suppletive clusivity distinction.

name: 1 sg
definition: The first-person singular pronominal stem, typically a reflex of PTB *ŋa or *ka.

name: thousand
definition: The natural number one thousand (1000).

name: 2 n sg
definition: Second person non-singular pronominal stem. This will not likely have a suppletive dual counterpart.

name: 2 sg
definition: The second-person singular pronominal stem, typically but not always a reflex of *naŋ.

name: 3 n sg
definition: Third person non-singular pronominal stem, unmarked for gender. If gendered forms are attested they should be added under separate concepts.

name: 3 sg
definition: Third person singular pronominal stem. This may in some cases also be one of the demonstrative stems, as is the case in much of Bodo-Garo.

name: to be above
definition: Situated in a higher place than something else.

name: Accipitridae (raptor)
definition: A bird of prey with broad wings and a hooked bill. Kites are the most common which occur in the area. This should be the most general term for this class of birds, and not a compound term for a specific species. Any specific genera/species names should be noted separately.
burmese: သိမ်းငှက်၊ လင်းယုန် သို့မဟုတ် စွန်ရဲ

name: adolescent
definition: Telating to or characteristic of adolescence, typically between 13 and 19 years old. This may not be attested in all languages, but is may reflect the age range prior to being a full adult.
burmese: ဆယ်ကျော်သက်

name: afternoon
definition: The part of the day which follows noon, between noon and evening.

name: to age (grow old)
definition: To age and become older.

name: age (of person)
definition: The length of time a person has been alive, usually measured in years.
burmese: လူတစ်ဦး၏အသက်

name: brewed alcohol
definition: A fermented drink is a beverage containing alcohol because of a metabolic process that converts sugar to acids, gases and/or alcohol (e.g. beer or wine).

name: distilled alcohol
definition: Alcoholic beverages made through distillation, such as whiskey or vodka. This will often be a borrowing, either from Tai or IA, though some varieties will retain a native form.
burmese: ပေါင်းခံအရက်

name: to be alive
definition: To have life and be living, not dead.
burmese: အသက်ရှင်ဖို့

name: all
definition: The whole quantity or extent of something. Or, everyone or everything considered together.

name: amber
definition: A hard, translucent fossilized resin, typically yellowish-brown in color. Used in some communities for ornaments such as earrings.

name: ancestors (general)
definition: The prople from whom one is descended, especially when more remote than a grandparent. This concept should be for figures which would not have been personally known by the speaker due to the distance in time.

name: to be angry
definition: Feeling or showing strong annoyance, displeasure, or hostility, usually toward someone or some thing.

name: female animal (affix)
definition: Of or denoting the sex that can bear offspring or produce eggs, distinguished biologically by the production of gametes (ova).
burmese: အမျိုးသမီး

name: male animal (affix)
definition: The marker used for animals which marks them as male.

name: animal (general)
definition: Any living organism characterized by voluntary movement, the possession of cells with noncellulose cell walls and specialized sense organs enabling rapid response to stimuli, and the ingestion of complex organic substances such as plants and other animals.

name: to respond
definition: To communicate in response to something.

name: to answer (question)
definition: To communicate a message of any form in reaction to something that has been asked or expressed, to the being who expressed it; to react verbally.

name: anthill
definition: A mound of earth made by ants as they dig their nest.
burmese: ပုရွက်ဆိတ်ကုန်း

name: termite
definition: A soft-bodied insect of the order Isoptera; individuals feed on cellulose and live in colonies with a caste system comprising three types of functional individuals: sterile workers and soldiers, and the reproductives.

name: ant (general)
definition: Any of the black, red, brown, or yellow insects of the family Formicidae characterized by a large head and by living in organized colonies.
burmese: ပုရွက်ဆိတ်

name: to be anxious
definition: Having the feeling of anxiety. To feel worried, uneasy, or nervous about something. Distinct from eagerness.

name: to apologise
definition: To express regret, remorse, sadness or accountability regarding something that one has done or failed to do.
burmese: စိတ်မကောင်းဖြစ်ရတယ်။

name: to appear
definition: To come into sight or become visible from being previously invisible or absent.

name: area under house
definition: The large space below a traditional stilt house, used for storage, keeping animals or building looms.
burmese: အုတ်တံတိုင်းအိမ်အောက် ဧရိယာ

name: areca nut
definition: The fruit of the areca palm, often chewed with betel leaf and other ingredients in many parts of Asia for its stimulant effects. Ofte called betel nut, but not coming from the same plant as the betel leaf.
comment: Concepticon has both BETEL NUTE and BETELNUT. This is marked as absent in Concepticon since betel is a different species, and the inconsistent labels in Concepticon create ambiguity.

name: armpit
definition: The hollow beneath the junction of the arm and shoulder.

name: upper arm
definition: The part of the arm between the shoulder and the elbow. This concept may not be present in many language varieties.
burmese: လက်မောင်းအပေါ်ပိုင်း

name: elbow
definition: The joint between the forearm and the upper arm.
burmese: တံတောင်ဆစ်

name: inner elbow
definition: The inner part of the elbow where the arm bends.
burmese: အတွင်းတံတောင်ဆစ်

name: forearm
definition: The part of the arm between the elbow and the wrist. This concept may not be present in many language varieties.

name: shoulder
definition: The joint connecting the upper arm and the torso, especially the top or outermost part.

name: wrist
definition: The joint connecting the hand and the forearm. This will typically be a compund involving the general hand/arm stem, and is likely to be entirely distinct from the term for elbow.
burmese: လက်ကောက်ဝတ်

name: arm (general)
definition: One of the two upper extremeties of the human body, extending from the shoulder to the wrist. This should be the most general term, and will often include the hand as well. A term for arm which does not include the hand is not expected.

name: to arrive
definition: To come to a destination.
burmese: ရောက်ရှိရန်

name: arrow
definition: Pointed projectile that is shot with a bow.

name: to ascend (move up)
definition: To move from a lower to a higher position by climbing. This should be distinct from the general go verbs which exist as part of systems of topographical deixis.
burmese: တက်ရန် သို့မဟုတ် တက်ရန်

name: ash
definition: The powdery incombustible residue left after the burning of a substance. Additional terms for different types of ash may be present, such as the stringy ash left over from burning dry bamboo. This concept is only for the most basic powdery type, but other forms should be documented as such.

name: ash (bamboo)
definition: The stringy type of ash which is characteristic of burning dried bamboo.

name: to be ashamed
definition: Feeling shame or guilt. This is distinct from being shy.

name: to ask (question)
definition: To inquire about something or express a desire or need for information about something. This is distinct from requesting action or requesting an item from someone.
burmese: တောင်းဆိုရန် သို့မဟုတ် တောင်းဆိုရန်

name: to awaken
definition: To stop sleeping and become conscious, to stir or come into awareness.

name: axe (general)
definition: A tool for felling trees or chopping wood consisting of a heavy metallic or stone head flattened to a blade on one side, and which is attached to a usually wooden handle.

name: back (of body)
definition: The rear surface of the human body from the shoulders to the hips.

name: back (side of something)
definition: The backward part or surface, as of a building.

name: to be bad
definition: Not good; unfavorable; negative.

name: bag
definition: A container made of flexible material with an opening at the top, used for carrying or storing items.

name: to be bald
definition: Without hair on the head.

name: bamboo
definition: A group of woody perennial evergreen plants in the true grass family Poaceae, subfamily Bambusoideae, tribe Bambuseae.

name: bamboo shoot
definition: The edible shoots (new bamboo culms that come out of the ground) of many bamboo species // Often harvested as part of local cuisine, either used fresh, dried or fermented.

name: bamboo skin
definition: The outer layer of a bamboo stalk, often used for making baskets and other woven goods.
burmese: ဝါးအရေပြား

name: bamboo strip
definition: A long, thin piece of bamboo used for various purposes.

name: bamboo tube
definition: A hollow tube made from a bamboo plant, used for carrying water, as a musical instrument, or for other utilitarian purposes.

name: banana (fruit)
definition: The fruit of the banana tree.

name: banana tree
definition: The tropical treelike plant which bears clusters of bananas. The plant, of the genus Musa, has large, elongated leaves.

name: banyan (tree)
definition: A large, tropical tree belonging to the genus Ficus, typically Ficus benghalensis, with aerial roots that grow into new trunks, often used for shade or as a spiritual symbol in many cultures.

name: to bark (dog)
definition: The loud often sharp vocalisation of a domestic dog.

name: firewood basket
definition: A basket primarily used for carrying firewood.

name: rice basket
definition: The type of basket primarily used to carry paddy.

name: small basket
definition: Any particularly small basket.

name: basket (general)
definition: The general term for any kind of basket, a container woven typically from cane or bamboo used to store or carry many different kinds of items or materials.

name: bat (animal)
definition: A small, flying mammal in the order Chiroptera with wings consisting of skin stretched over a framework of bones, typically active at night.

name: beak (bill)
definition: The hard, pointed mouthpart of a bird, used for eating, grooming, and other activities.

name: beam (rafter)
definition: A typically horizontal piece of wood or steel that supports the weight of a building, typically running from one side of the building to the other.
burmese: အိမ်တစ်အိမ်၏အလင်းတန်း

name: bean (general)
definition: Any of various leguminous plants grown for their edible seeds and pods.

name: bear (animal)
definition: A large beast of prey of the family Ursidae, related to the dog and raccoon, having shaggy hair, a very small tail, and flat feet.

name: to bear (fruit)
definition: To produce or yield fruits.

name: beard
definition: Facial hair of humans on the chin, cheeks and jaw.
burmese: မုတ်ဆိတ်မွေး

name: to beat (someone)
definition: To strike or pound repeatedly, usually in some sort of rhythm.

name: bed
definition: A piece of furniture used for sleeping or resting, typically consisting of a mattress and a frame.

name: beehive
definition: A structure that provides a natural habitation for bees; as in a hollow tree.

name: beeswax
definition: A yellowish or dark brown wax secreted by honeybees for constructing honeycombs.

name: bee (general)
definition: Any pollenating flying insect belonging to the Anthophila clade within the order Hymenoptera. Typically having yellow and black colouring with a striped pattern on the abdoment.

name: bee colony
definition: The honeycombed colony structure where bees live and produce honey.

name: to beg
definition: To ask for something, typically money or food, as charity or as a favor. This may be either due to need through poverty, or as an act of religious devotion such as among Buddhist monks.
burmese: တောင်းရမ်းရန်

name: to be behind (something)
definition: At or to the far side of something, typically so as to be hidden from view. Alternatively, on the back side of some person or thing from the frame of reference of that person or thing thing.

name: belly (exterior)
definition: The lower part of the front of the torso (or a comparable part of an animal), confined by the upper side by the midriff and the lowerside by the pelvis. Contains the intestines.
burmese: ဗိုက်၊အပြင်

name: to be below (under)
definition: Situated in a lower place than something else.

name: to be big
definition: Of great size or extent relative to some other thing.

name: to bind (hands)
definition: To tie or fasten something together with a rope, cord, or other material, to restrict or constrain something or someone.
burmese: ချည်နှောင်ရန်

name: bird (general term)
definition: Any of the bipedal, warm-blooded vertebrates that lay eggs having wings which, for most species, enables them to fly.
burmese: ငှက်၊ ယေဘူယျ

name: to bite
definition: Clamping the teeth hard on something.

name: to be bitter
definition: Having an acrid taste, typical of citrus peel or bitter gourd Momordica charantia.

name: blanket
definition: A large piece of fabric or covering used for warmth, typically on a bed or to wrap around oneself.

name: to be blind
definition: Unable to see, either partially or completely.
burmese: မျက်မမြင်ဖြစ်ရန်

name: blister
definition: A small bubble on the skin, that contains watery fluid and is caused by heat, pressure or infection.

name: to block (obstruct)
definition: To obstruct or prevent something from passing through or being seen.
burmese: ပိတ်ဆို့ရန်

name: blood
definition: A fluid connective tissue consisting of the plasma and cells that circulate in the blood vessels.

name: to bloom
definition: To bear flowers or to start bearing flowers; to blossom.
burmese: ပန်းတစ်ပွင့်၊

name: to blow (wind)
definition: (Of the wind or a current of air) To move.

name: to blow (with mouth)
definition: To expel air through persed lips.

name: to be blunt (of edge)
definition: Not having a sharp edge.

name: to be blunt (of point)
definition: Not having a sharp point.

name: boat
definition: A craft used for transportation of goods, fishing, racing, recreational cruising, or military use on or in the water, propelled by oars or outboard motor or inboard motor or by wind.
burmese: သင်္ဘော သို့မဟုတ် လှေ

name: body
definition: The physical structure of a human or animal, including the bones, flesh, and organs.
burmese: ခန္ဓာကိုယ်

name: to boil (liquid)
definition: To reach or cause to reach the temperature at which a liquid bubbles and turns to vapor by adding heat.

name: bone
definition: Any of the components of an endoskeleton, consisting mainly of calcium phosphate, collagen and cells.

name: bone marrow
definition: The spongy tissue in the hollow parts of bones.
burmese: ရိုးတွင်းခြင်ဆီ

name: to be born
definition: To come into existence, typically through childbirth.

name: Bos frontalis (mithun)
definition: A member of the Bos genus having a large size and posessing characteristic horns with a wide base. Important draught animal for local agriculture.

name: Bos gaurus (gaur)
definition: A large, dark-coated wild ox found in Southeast Asia and the Indian Subcontinent.

name: bow
definition: A weapon made of a curved piece of wood or other flexible material whose ends are connected by a string, used for shooting arrows, or a weapon based on it, consisting of a bow mounted on a stock.
comment: this should be split between bow and crossbow probably.

name: to bow
definition: To bend the body forward or downward as a sign of respect or greeting, to curve or bend into a particular shape.
burmese: ဦးညွှတ်ရန်

name: crossbow
definition: A weapon based on the bow, consisting of a bow mounted on a stock.

name: bowl
definition: A roughly hemispherical container used to hold, mix or present food, such as salad, fruit or soup, or other items.

name: bracelet
definition: Piece of jewellery worn around the wrist.

name: brain
definition: The organ of the central nervous system of an animal or human located in the skull that controls the actions and thoughts of the animal or human.

name: to break (something)
definition: To come apart or split into pieces (intransitive).

name: breast
definition: The fleshy organ on the chest of a sexually mature human female containing mammary glands.

name: to breathe
definition: To repeatedly draw air into, and expel it from, the lungs, in order to extract oxygen from it and excrete waste products.
burmese: အသက်ရှူရန်

name: bridge
definition: A structure that spans and provides a passage over a road, railway, river, or some other obstacle.

name: to be bright
definition: Emitting or reflecting light readily or in large amounts. [WN:679]
burmese: တောက်ပ၊ အလင်း

name: to bring
definition: To transport toward somewhere; to take something or somebody with oneself somewhere.

name: broom
definition: A tool used to sweep and clean the floor, made of a bundle of straws or twigs attached to a long handle.
burmese: တံမြက်စည်း

name: elder brother
definition: A male with more years of age than one or more of his siblings.
burmese: အစ်ကိုအကြီး

name: younger brother
definition: A male with fewer years of age than one or more of his siblings.

name: Bubalus bubalis (water buffalo)
definition: A large bovid originating in South Asia, Southeast Asia, and China.

name: bundle
definition: A collection of objects, typically tied together, for ease of carrying or storage. In the case of firewood, it refers to a bundle of sticks or logs used as fuel for a fire.
burmese: ထင်းကဲ့သို့ အစုအဝေး၊

name: to burn (intransitive)
definition: To put fire on something or to be on fire.

name: to burrow
definition: To dig a hole or tunnel in the ground, of animals which reside in such holes.
burmese: တွင်းတူးရန်

name: to bury (object)
definition: To put in the ground and cover with earth.
burmese: သင်္ဂြိုဟ်ရန်

name: butterfly
definition: A lepidopteran that is active at day.

name: to buy
definition: To obtain in exchange for money or goods.

name: cane (rattan)
definition: Material from rattan palms which is used to create furniture.

name: to carry (general)
definition: To lift and bring to somewhere else; to transport by lifting.
burmese: သယ်ဆောင်ရန်

name: to carry (in arms)
definition: To carry something in ones arms. This concept will typically overlap with the general carry term, but occurs separately here in cases where there may be a difference.

name: to carry (in hand)
definition: To hold or to take something from one place to another by hands.

name: to carry (in pocket)
definition: To hold or to take something from one place to another on the back.

name: to carry (on head)
definition: To hold or to take something from one place to another on top of the head.

name: to carry (on pole)
definition: The act of transporting something by means of a carrying pole placed on one's shoulder.

name: to carry (on shoulder)
definition: To hold or to take something from one place to another on one shoulder.

name: to carry (under arm)
definition: To hold or to take something from one place to another under the arm.

name: to carve
definition: To cut or to chip in order to form something.
burmese: ထွင်းထုရန်

name: cat (domestic)
definition: A common four-legged animal (Felis silvestris) that is often kept as a household pet.

name: cattle (domestic)
definition: Domesticated bovine animals, including cows, steers and bulls, raised and bred on a ranch or farm.

name: cave
definition: A large underground chamber or network of chambers.

name: centre (middle)
definition: The middle of an object or places area, such as a target or focal point.
burmese: အလယ်၊ ဗဟို

name: charcoal
definition: The blackish residue consisting of carbon and any remaining ash left after the slow burning of wood or other organic matter in an oxygen-starved environment.

name: cheek
definition: The soft skin on each side of the face, between the eyes and the chin; the outer surface of the sides of the oral cavity.

name: chest
definition: The portion of the body from the base of the neck to the top of the abdomen; the thorax.

name: to chew
definition: To crush with the teeth by repeated closing and opening of the jaws; done to food to soften it and break it down by the action of saliva before it is swallowed.

name: chicken
definition: A type of domesticated bird from the order of Galliformes which is often raised as a type of poultry (Gallus gallus domesticus).

name: child (general)
definition: A young human being below the age of puberty or below the legal age of majority.
burmese: ကလေး၊ မွေးကင်းစ

name: chili pepper
definition: Any fruit of a plant of the botanical genus Capsicum, noted for their spicy and burning flavour due to presence of capsaicin.
burmese: ငရုတ်သီးမှုန့်

name: chin
definition: The bottom of the face, below the mouth.

name: chisel (n)
definition: A tool with a sharp edge at the end, used for cutting or carving hard materials.

name: to choose (between things)
definition: To make a choice from a number of alternatives.
burmese: ရွေးချယ်ရန်

name: cicada
definition: Insects in the order Hemiptera, suborder Auchenorrhyncha.
burmese: ပုစဉ်းရင်ကွဲ

name: civet cat
definition: A carnivorous mammal of the Viverridae family, found across South East Asia. // Often kept for its musky-scented secretion.

name: claw (animal)
definition: The hard, keratin part growing at the feet of animals.

name: clay
definition: A loose, earthy, extremely fine-grained, natural sediment or soft rock composed primarily of clay-size or colloidal particles and characterized by high plasticity and by a considerable content of clay mineral and subordinate amounts of finely divided quartz, decomposed feldspar, carbonates, ferruginous matter, and other impurities; it forms a plastic, moldable mass when finely ground and mixed with water, retains its shape on drying, and becomes firm, rocklike and permanently hard on heating or firing.

name: to clean
definition: To cause something to be no longer dirty.
burmese: သန့်ရှင်းရန်

name: to be clear (in meaning)
definition: To be easy to understand or see.
burmese: ရှင်းရှင်းလင်းလင်းဖြစ်ရန်

name: to close (tr)
definition: To shut or cover the entrance or opening of something, preventing access or exit.

name: cloth
definition: A woven fabric such as used in dressing, decorating, cleaning or other practical use.

name: cloud (rain)
definition: A visible mass of condensed water vapor floating in the atmosphere, typically high above the ground.

name: cockroach
definition: The most primitive of the living winged insects. // A brown or black insect with a flattened body and long antennae, often considered a pest.

name: to coddle
definition: To treat someone in an indulgent or overprotective way.

name: to be cold (of items)
definition: Having a low temperature.

name: to be cold (of weather)
definition: Having a low temperature (of the weather).
burmese: ရာသီဥတုအေး

name: to be black
definition: Of the very darkest color owing to the absence of or complete absorption of light, the opposite of white.

name: to be green
definition: Having green as its colour; having the hue of that portion of the visible spectrum lying between yellow and blue, evoked in the human observer by radiant energy with wavelengths of approximately 490 to 570 nanometers.
burmese: အစိမ်းရောင်

name: to be grey
definition: Having a colour between black and white, like ash or stone.

name: to be red
definition: A color resembling the hue of blood, fire, or a ripe tomato.

name: to be white
definition: A color characterized by the presence of all wavelengths of visible light, often associated with purity or innocence.

name: to be yellow
definition: Having the colour of a yolk, a lemon or gold.

name: Columbidae (pigeon)
definition: A type of bird belonging to Columbidae, often found in cities and commonly used in racing and as a pet.

name: comb
definition: A toothed implement for grooming the hair.

name: to comb
