name: hide (oneself)
definition: To put oneself in a place where one cannot be found.
burmese: ထမင်းထောင်း

name: to be high
definition: Being in a position comparatively far above to the ground.
burmese: မြင့်မားရန်

name: hip
definition: The outward-projecting parts of the pelvis and top of the femur and the overlying tissue.

name: to hit (something)
definition: To hit against with a sharp blow or to impel, usually with a hand or weapon or to be forcefully or suddenly contacting, e.g. a tree falling down and hitting the ground.
burmese: ရိုက်နှက်ရန်

name: to hold (in hand)
definition: To grasp or grip (particularly with the hand) so that the object does not end up at the surface below.
burmese: လက်၌ကိုင်ထားရန်

name: hole (general)
definition: A hollow place in a solid body or surface.

name: honey
definition: A viscous, sweet substance produced from nectar or honeydew by bees.

name: hook
definition: A rod bent into a curved shape, for catching, holding, or sustaining anything.

name: horizon
definition: The apparent line that separates earth from sky, the line that divides all visible directions into two categories: those that intersect the Earth's surface, and those that do not.
burmese: မိုးကုပ်စက်ဝိုင်း

name: horn (of animal)
definition: A hard growth of keratin that protrudes from the top of the head of certain animals.

name: great hornbill
definition: Buceros bicornis, the large varieties of hornbill common to the region.

name: small hornbill
definition: Smaller varieties of hornbill.

name: hornbill (general)
definition: A bird characterized by a long, down-curved, and frequently colored beak.

name: horse (general)
definition: A large animal with four legs of the Equus caballus species which people ride on or use for carrying things or pulling vehicles.

name: to be hot
definition: Having, giving off, or producing a high degree of heat.

name: to be hot (of weather)
definition: A period of unusually high temperatures.
burmese: ရာသီဥတုပူ၊

name: house
definition: A building for human habitation, especially one that is lived in by a family or small group of people.

name: housefly (common)
definition: A common insect; any species of insect of the order Diptera.

name: to be hungry
definition: To be in need of food.
burmese: ဆာလောင်မှုကိုခံစားရရန်

name: to hunt
definition: To chase down prey and (usually) kill it.
burmese: အမဲလိုက်ရန်

name: husband
definition: The male partner in a marriage.

name: to ignite (something)
definition: To start a fire or light a flame.
burmese: မီးလောင်ရန်

name: to be ill (sick)
definition: To be in poor health, suffering from a physical or mental condition that causes discomfort or pain.
burmese: နေမကောင်းဖြစ်ခြင်း။

name: to be in front of
definition: To be situated or placed before or ahead of.

name: insect
definition: A class of the Arthropoda typically having a segmented body with an external chitinous covering, a pair of compound eyes, a pair of antennae, three pairs of mouthparts, and two pairs of wings.

name: beetle
definition: A group of insects which are biologically classified in the order Coleoptera /koʊliːˈɒptərə/.

name: to play instrument
definition: Execute coordinated movements on or with a musical instrument to produce sounds.
burmese: သီချင်းဖွင့်ရန်

name: intestines
definition: The alimentary canal of an animal or human through which food passes after having passed all stomachs.

name: iron
definition: A malleable ductile silvery-white ferromagnetic metallic element with symbol Fe and atomic number 26, occurring principally in haematite and magnetite. It is widely used for structural and engineering purposes.

name: island
definition: A land mass, especially one smaller than a continent, entirely surrounded by water.

name: to be itchy
definition: Having a sensation that provokes the need to scratch.

name: jackal
definition: A wild dog-like animal of the Canis genus home to parts of Asia and Africa.

name: jaw
definition: Either of the two opposable structures forming, or near the entrance to, the mouth.

name: joint (skeletal)
definition: The point where two bones meet, allowing movement and flexibility.
burmese: ခန္ဓာကိုယ်၏အဆစ်

name: jug
definition: A container for holding and pouring liquids with a handle and a spout.

name: juice (of fruit)
definition: The liquid that is produced by squeezing or crushing fruits or vegetables.

name: to jump
definition: To propel oneself rapidly upward such that momentum causes the body to become airborne.

name: jungle
definition: Unmaintained wild forest or shrubland which has not im a state of cultivation. This can be part of old growth forest or the quickly speading vegetation which has taken over a fallow field.

name: jute (plant, fibre)
definition: A plant native to Asia used for its fiber, which is commonly used to make rope and burlap.

name: kapok
definition: Either the Bombax ceiba (tree with red flowers), or the Calotropis procera, or the Ceiba pentandra.

name: to keep
definition: To retain possession of something.
burmese: ထိန်းသိမ်းရန်၊ ထိန်းသိမ်းရန်

name: to kick (and propel)
definition: To kick something so as to propel it.

name: to kick (stationary item)
definition: To strike something stationary with the foot.

name: to kill
definition: To put to death; to end a life.

name: to kneel
definition: To go down on one or both knees.
burmese: ဒူးထောက်ရန်

name: knife
definition: A utensil consisting of a sharpened piece of hard material such as steel or other metal, ceramic, glass or stone, usually attached to a handle, that is formed in a manner that allows for cutting softer materials, especially meat or other food.

name: edge of knife
definition: The sharp cutting edge of a knife.

name: to know (how)
definition: To be able to do something which requires or could require that one would learn it before.
burmese: တစ်ခုခုလုပ်နည်းသိရန်

name: to know (someone)
definition: To be familiar with a person, primarily through having previously met them face to face.
burmese: တစ်ခုခုသိဖို့

name: to know (something)
definition: To have knowledge or comprehension of something through learning or experience.
burmese: တစ်ခုခုကိုနားလည်ရန်

name: to lack
definition: To lack something or to describe the state when something is not there.

name: ladder (stairs)
definition: A series of steps or stairs that allow a person to move from one level or floor to another. This is meant primarily as the traditional log ladders, but this may differ based on differences in house construction practices.

name: lake
definition: An enclosed body of water, usually but not necessarily fresh water, from which the sea is excluded.

name: land (area)
definition: An area of ground or soil, especially in a particular context or for a particular purpose.

name: language
definition: A system of communication using the spoken or signed word or using symbols that represent words, signs or sounds.

name: to be late
definition: Occurring or arriving after the expected or usual time, or toward the end of a time period.
burmese: နေ့ဘက်နောက်ကျမည်။

name: to laugh
definition: To express pleasure, mirth or derision by peculiar movement of the muscles of the face, particularly of the mouth, causing a lighting up of the face and eyes, and usually accompanied by the emission of explosive or chuckling sounds from the chest and throat.

name: layer
definition: A thin sheet, film, or coating of material, cloth or soil. Any horizontally oriented layer distinct from others.
burmese: တစ်ခုခု၏အလွှာ

name: to be lazy
definition: Unwilling to do work or make an effort.

name: leaf (tree)
definition: The main organ of photosynthesis and transpiration in higher plants, usually consisting of a flat green blade attached to the stem directly or by a stalk.

name: to learn
definition: To acquire, or attempt to acquire knowledge or an ability to do something.

name: leather
definition: The dressed or tanned hide of an animal, usually with the hair removed.

name: aquatic leech
definition: A worm-like creature that lives in water and sucks blood from animals.

name: terrestrial leech
definition: Segmented worms that belong to the phylum Annelida and comprise the subclass Hirudinea.

name: left side
definition: The side of the body to the west when facing north.

name: ankle
definition: A joint formed where the foot and the leg meet.
burmese: ခြေချင်းဝတ်

name: calf
definition: The fleshy backside of the lower part of the leg.

name: foot
definition: The part of a human’s body below the ankle that is used in order to stand and walk.

name: knee
definition: The joint between the thigh and the lower leg in humans.

name: knee pit
definition: The hollow or depression at the back of the knee.
burmese: ဒူး၏နောက်ဘက်

name: shin
definition: The front part of the leg below the knee.

name: thigh
definition: The area of the leg between the hip and the knee.

name: to be level
definition: To lack any discernable slope or incline, running perpendicular to the pull of gravity.

name: to lick
definition: To pass the tongue over something in order to taste or wet it.

name: to lie (decieve)
definition: To knowingly say something that is untrue.

name: to lie down
definition: (For a human or animal) to assume a horizontally extended position on a surface.

name: to lift
definition: To cause an object to have a higher location than previously.
burmese: လွှင့်တင်ရန်

name: lightning (in sky)
definition: The flash of light caused by the discharge of atmospheric electrical charge.

name: to be lightweight
definition: With a small mass, little weight or density; the opposite of heavy.
burmese: ပေါ့ပါးစေရန်

name: lime (betelnut)
definition: A calcium-containing inorganic material in which carbonates, oxides and hydroxides predominate.
burmese: သံပုရာသီး (ပစ္စည်း)

name: lip (of mouth)
definition: Either of the two fleshy protrusions around the opening of the mouth.

name: liquid
definition: A substance that flows freely but is of constant volume, having a consistency like that of water or oil.

name: to listen
definition: To perceive with the ear (paying attention to what is heard).

name: liver
definition: A large organ in the body that stores and metabolizes nutrients, destroys toxins and produces bile. Responsible for thousands of biochemical reactions.

name: monitor lizard
definition: A large, carnivorous lizard of the family Varanidae, native to Asia and Africa.

name: lizard (general)
definition: Any reptile of the suborder Lacertilia, especially those of the family Lacertidae, typically having an elongated body, four limbs, and a small tail: includes the gechos, iguanas, chameleons, monitors, and slow worms.

name: locust
definition: Migratory grasshoppers of the order Orthoptera of warm regions having short antennae.

name: log
definition: A length of a thick, heavy, and durable piece of timber, especially one that has fallen or been cut from a tree.

name: to be long
definition: Having much distance from one terminating point on an object or an area to another terminating point.

name: to look at
definition: To direct one's gaze in a specified direction.
burmese: တစ်ခုခုကိုကြည့်ဖို့

name: to look for (seek)
definition: To try to find something or someone.

name: loom
definition: A frame or machine (made of wood or other material) in which a weaver forms cloth out of thread; a machine for interweaving yarn or threads into a fabric.
burmese: ရက်ကန်းစင်

name: to be loose
definition: Being not tight.

name: to lose (something)
definition: To be unable to find something; To be deprived of something which one once had.

name: to be lost
definition: Not knowing where you are and unable to find the way.

name: to be loud
definition: (Of a sound) to have a high volume.
burmese: အသံကျယ်ဖို့

name: louse
definition: A small wingless parasitic insect of the order Phthiraptera that lives on humans, other mammals and birds.

name: to love
definition: To have an intense feeling of affection and care towards another person.

name: lung
definition: A biological organ that extracts oxygen from the air.

name: machete (dao)
definition: A large, heavy knife used for cutting through thick vegetation or used as a weapon. This concept should refer to the most typical cutting implement, known as the Dao or Dha in contact languages, which is widely carried, and not one of the various alternate forms used for chopping wood or other tasks.

name: old man
definition: A male person who is old of age.

name: man (male person)
definition: An adult human male.

name: mango
definition: A sweet tropical fruit with a soft yellowish-red skin and juicy yellow flesh.

name: to be many
definition: An indefinite large number of.

name: to mark (something)
definition: To make a visible impression or trace on something, to indicate or show something.
burmese: အမှတ်အသားလုပ်ဖို့

name: market
definition: Place of commercial activity in which articles are bought and sold.

name: to marry
definition: To enter marriage; to take a husband or a wife.

name: mat
definition: A flat object laid on the floor to protect a person from the hard floor. Typically woven from cane, bamboo or fibers.

name: match (stick)
definition: A stick with inflammable substance on one end that can be set on fire by friction.
burmese: ပွဲစဉ်တစ်ခု

name: meat (flesh)
definition: The edible flesh of animals, especially that of mammals.

name: medicine
definition: A substance or preparation used for the treatment or prevention of disease, or for maintaining or restoring health.

name: to meet (someone)
definition: To encounter a person, either intentionally or by chance.

name: to mend
definition: To restore something by replacing a broken part or putting together what is broken.
burmese: ပြုပြင်ရန် သို့မဟုတ် ပြုပြင်ရန်

name: metal
definition: A material (an element, compound, or alloy) that is typically hard, opaque, shiny, and has good electrical and thermal conductivity.

name: midway
definition: Being half the distance to something or between two things.

name: milk
definition: The whitish fluid secreted by the mammary gland for the nourishment of the young; composed of carbohydrates, proteins, fats, mineral salts, vitamins, and antibodies.

name: mill
definition: A machine used for grinding grains into flour.

name: finger millet
definition: Eleusine coracana, a herbaceous plant characteristic for the hability to withstand cultivation at high altitudes.

name: foxtail millet
definition: Staria italica, an annual grass grown for human food and related to (broomcorn) millet.

name: millet (general)
definition: A group of small-seeded species of cereal crops, widely grown around the world for food and fodder.
burmese: ပြောင်းဆန်

name: to make mistake
definition: To do something incorrectly or inaccurately.
burmese: အမှားလုပ်ရန်

name: money
definition: A medium of exchange in the form of coins, banknotes, or digital currency.

name: langur
definition: A type of long-tailed monkey found in South and Southeast Asia.

name: monkey (general)
definition: A mammal with a long tail, a small face, and usually hands and feet adapted for grasping and climbing.

name: month
definition: A period into which a year is divided, historically based on the phases of the moon. In the Gregorian calendar there are twelve months.

name: moon
definition: A natural satellite of a planet.

name: full moon
definition: The lunar phase when the moon is fully illuminated by the sun and appears in the sky as a full circle.

name: half moon
definition: The phase of the moon in which it is equally illuminated and in shadow, halfway between a new moon and full moon.
burmese: ကမ္ဘာဂြိုဟ်

name: new moon
definition: The lunar phase when the moon appears in the sky as a slender crescent shortly after its conjunction with the sun.

name: morning
definition: The period of time from the start of the day (midnight) until midday (12:00).

name: mortar
definition: A bowl used to crush and grind ingredients with a pestle.

name: mosquito
definition: A small flying insect (of the family Culicidae) known for biting and sucking blood.

name: moth
definition: Group of insects related to butterflies.

name: mother
definition: A woman who has at least one child.

name: mountain
definition: A feature of the earth's surface that rises high above the base and has generally steep slopes and a relatively small summit area.

name: foot of mountain
definition: Lower part in front of a mountain, before the mountain begins.
burmese: တောင်ခြေရင်း

name: cliff
definition: A steep coastal declivity which may or may not be precipitous, the slope angle being dependent partly on the jointing, bedding and hardness of the materials from which the cliff has been formed, and partly on the erosional processes at work.(Source: WHIT)

name: foothills
definition: The uneven lowlands between the plains and the mountains.

name: slope
definition: A very steep decline, typically found in the mountains or on shores, or a stretch of ground forming a geological incline, e.g. a hillside.

name: mountain peak (summit)
definition: The highest point on top of a mountain or hill.

name: mountain range
definition: A series of mountains or hills, often connected by high ground.

name: mountain ridge
definition: A geological feature consisting of a chain of mountains or hills that form a continuous elevated crest for some distance.

name: mouse
definition: Any of numerous small rodents of the genus ''mus'' or various related genera of the ''Muridæ'' family characterised by a long hairless tail, rounded ears, and a pointed nose.

name: mouth
definition: Opening in the lower half of a human face which is used for food ingestion and articulation.

name: mud
definition: A soft, wet, sticky mixture of soil and water, such as is formed after the rain.

name: muroid
definition: A large superfamily of rodents, including hamsters, gerbils, true mice and rats, and many other relatives.
burmese: ကြွက်၊အထွေထွေအသုံးအနှုန်း

name: muscle
definition: An organ formed by contractile tissue that moves other organs.

name: mushroom (ground type)
definition: A type of mushroom that grows in the soil, rather than on trees.

name: mushroom (tree type)
definition: A type of mushroom that grows on or near trees, and often has a stalk and cap.
burmese: သစ်ပင်မှို

name: mustard seed
definition: Brassica juncea. A plant whose seeds are used to make a spice, oil or condiment. Most commonly used for oil production.
comment: CONCEPTICON refers to the sauce, not the seed or plant

name: crested myna
definition: A species of starling native to southeastern China and Indochina.

name: myna (common)
definition: A type of bird known for its ability to mimic sounds and speech.

name: nail
definition: A small, thin piece of metal or other material used to fasten objects together.

name: to be naked
definition: Without clothing.
burmese: အဝတ်အချည်းစည်းဖြစ်

name: name
definition: Any word or phrase which designates a particular person, place, class or thing.

name: to be narrow
definition: Not wide, having little width or space between two sides or edges.

name: navel
definition: A scar where the umbilical cord was attached.

name: to be near
definition: Not far distant in time or space or degree or circumstances.

name: neck
definition: The part of the body (found in some animals, including humans) that connects the head and the trunk.

name: nape of neck
definition: The back part of the neck.
burmese: လည်ပင်း၏လည်ကုပ်

name: neck (thyroid area)
definition: The part of the neck where the thyroid gland is located.
burmese: လည်ပင်းသိုင်းရွိုက်ဧရိယာ

name: necklace
definition: An article of jewelry that is worn around the neck.

name: needle
definition: A thin, sharp implement used in sewing, knitting and acupuncture.

name: neighbour
definition: A person living in a house that is adjacent or nearby another person's house.
burmese: အိမ်နီးချင်း

name: bird nest
definition: A nest in which birds lay and hatch their eggs.

name: fishing net
definition: A piece of fabric or mesh made of threads, cords or ropes that are woven or knotted together with spaces between them, used for catching fish or other animals, or for protecting or separating things.

name: to be new
definition: Recently made, created or begun.
burmese: အသစ်ဖြစ်ရန်

name: night
definition: The period between sunset and sunrise, when a location faces far away from the sun, thus when the sky is dark.

name: to be noisy (boisterous)
definition: To make a lot of noise.
burmese: ဆူညံနေပါစေ။

name: noon (midday)
definition: Time of day when the sun is in its zenith.
burmese: နေ့လယ်၊ နေ့လယ်

name: north
definition: One of the four major compass points, specifically 0°, directed toward the North Pole, and conventionally upwards on a map.

name: nose
definition: The organ of the face used to breath and smell.

name: nostril
definition: Either of the two orifices located on the nose (or on the beak of a bird); used as a passage for air and other gases to travel the nasal passages.

name: to occur (happen)
definition: To take place, occur or come about.
burmese: ဖြစ်ပေါ်လာရန်၊

name: to offer (something)
definition: To present or give something as a gift or sacrifice, or to propose or suggest something for consideration.

name: oil (substance)
definition: A liquid or semi-solid substance that is used for frying, sautéing, or baking food, or for greasing pans or grills.
burmese: ချက်ပြုတ်ရန်အတွက် ဆီ သို့မဟုတ် ဆီ

name: to be old (of people)
definition: To have existed or been in use for a long time, having lived or existed for a long time.
burmese: အသက်ကြီးရန်
comment: Both CONCEPTICON forms refer to people, not things.

name: onion
definition: A vegetable and is the most widely cultivated species of the genus Allium.
burmese: ကြက်သွန်နီ

name: to open (tr)
definition: To make the inside something accessible by moving an obstacle aside (e.g. a door or covering), or to move said obstacle.
burmese: ဖွင့်လှစ်ရန်

name: orchid
definition: Any of the genera of flowering plants within Orchidaceae with a showy, often colorful, flower.

name: origin
definition: The source or beginning of something.

name: otter
definition: Any of several aquatic, furbearing, weasellike mammals of the genus Lutra, having webbed feet and a long, slightly flattened tail.

name: outside
definition: In the open, not within a building, or outside of something in general.

name: outsider (foreigner)
definition: A person who does not belong to a particular group or community.

name: overmorrow
definition: On the day following tomorrow.

name: owl
definition: A solitary, mainly nocturnal bird of prey, belonging to the order Strigiformes; it has large forward-facing eyes and ears and a hawk-like beak, and it can turn its head 180 degrees around.

name: ox
definition: A domesticated bovine animal used as a draft animal or for meat, milk, or leather.

name: to pack (things)
definition: To put something in a container so that it could be carried or transported.
burmese: တိရစ္ဆာန်များထုပ်ပိုး

name: palm tree
definition: Any of various evergreen trees from the family Palmae or Arecaceae, which are mainly found in the tropics.

name: pangolin
definition: Mammals of the order Pholidota. The one extant family, Manidae, has three genera: Manis which comprises four species living in Asia, Phataginus which comprises two species living in Africa, and Smutsia which comprises two species also living in Africa.
burmese: သင်းခွေချပ်

name: parents (general)
definition: The people who has given birth to or raised a child, typically involving both a mother and father in traditional families in the region.

name: parrot
definition: Any bird of the order Psittaciformes. This will typically be the Vernal Hanging-Parrot Loriculus vernalis, a mostly green species with bits of read which lives high in the canopy.
burmese: ကြက်တူရွေး

name: side of path
definition: The edge of a road, usually marked by a line or curb, that separates the road from the sidewalk or adjacent land.
burmese: လမ်းတစ်ဘက်

name: path (road)
definition: A thoroughfare or track that is used for traveling from one place to another, typically by foot or vehicle.
burmese: လမ်း သို့မဟုတ် လမ်း

name: to pay
definition: To give money in exchange for goods or services.

name: peacock
definition: A male peafowl, a species of the family Phasianidae, which is known for displaying its massive tail as part of mate-selection ritual.

name: to peel
definition: To remove the outer layer or skin of something.
burmese: အခွံချွတ်ရန်

name: penis
definition: The male sexual organ for copulation and urination; the tubular portion of the male genitalia (excluding the scrotum).

name: people
definition: Human beings as a group, including their customs, culture, and social structures.

name: to perch
definition: To sit or rest on a perch or elevated spot, typically of a bird or other animal.

name: old person
definition: Of a person, having lived for a long time or being advanced in age.

name: person (human)
definition: A human being.

name: pestle
definition: A heavy cylindrical object with a rounded end used for crushing and grinding.

name: pheasant
definition: Bird of the family Phasianidae.

name: to pick (of fruit)
definition: To remove small pieces from the surface of something using fingers or a tool.

name: to pierce (puncture)
definition: To make a hole or wound in something using a sharp object.
burmese: ဖောက်ရန် သို့မဟုတ် ထိုးရန်

name: pig (general)
definition: A common, four-legged animal (Sus scrofa) that has cloven hooves, bristles and a nose adapted for digging and is farmed by humans for its meat.

name: pillar
definition: A large vertical structure used to support a building or other structure.

name: pillow
definition: A cushion or other object used to support the head while sleeping or resting. Occasionally found in the form of a bamboo segment cut in half lengthwise.

name: place (area)
definition: A position or area in a space.

name: to place (put)
definition: To set or place an object somewhere.
burmese: တစ်စုံတစ်ခုကို ထားရန်၊

name: plain (unadorned)
definition: Simple and without decoration or embellishment.
burmese: ရိုးရိုး၊ မအလှဆင်

name: plains (lowlands)
definition: Land that is low or close to sea level.

name: plank (wood)
definition: A long, narrow, flat piece of wood used for building houses or other structures.
burmese: သစ်သားပျဉ် သို့မဟုတ် ဘုတ်ပြား

name: plant
definition: Any living organism that synthesizes its food from inorganic substances, possesses cellulose cell walls, responds slowly and often permanently to a stimulus, lacks specialized sense organs and nervous system, and has no powers of locomotion.
burmese: အပင်တစ်ပင်

name: to plant
definition: To put a plant in the ground so that it strikes root and grows.

name: to plant (with stick)
definition: To insert a stick or similar object into the ground to create a hole for a plant to be placed in.
burmese: တုတ်ဖြင့်စိုက်ရန်

name: plate
definition: A flat dish on which food is served or from which food is eaten.

name: to play (game)
definition: To act in a manner such that one has fun; to engage in playful activities expressly for the purpose of recreation.

name: plough
definition: A farm tool used to prepare soil for planting by breaking up and turning over the earth.

name: to plough
definition: To use a plough on to prepare for planting.
burmese: ထွန်ယက်ရန်

name: to poison
definition: To administer or introduce poison into a living organism, often with the intention of causing harm or death.

name: poison (for arrow)
definition: A substance which, when ingested, inhaled, or absorbed, or when applied to, injected into, or developed within the body, in relatively small amounts, may cause injury, harm, or destruction to organs, tissue, or life.

name: pond
definition: A natural body of standing fresh water occupying a small surface depression, usually smaller than a lake and larger than a pool.

name: porcupine
definition: Rodents with a coat of sharp spines, or quills, that protect against predators.

name: porcupine quill
definition: The term for an individual spine or quill of a porcupine. An important cultural artefact relating to fashion in some communities.

name: post
definition: A strong upright piece of wood, metal etc. that is fixed into the ground, especially to support something.
burmese: ချည်ပို့စ်

name: cooking pot
definition: A vessel used for cooking or storing food or liquids.
burmese: ဟင်းချက်အိုး

name: earthen pot
definition: A vessel used for cooking or storing food or liquids, made of baked mud or clay.

name: to pound (of rice)
definition: To break into small pieces or powder by applying force with a tool, or to reduce something to small particles by rubbing it against a rough or hard surface.

name: to pour
definition: To cause a liquid to flow out from a container.

name: to be prepared
definition: Prepared for immediate action or use.
burmese: အဆင်သင့်ဖြစ်ရန်

name: to press
definition: To apply force or weight onto something.

name: to be proud
definition: Feeling greatly pleased, or satisfied by something or someone that is highly honorable or creditable to oneself.
burmese: ဂုဏ်ယူဖို့

name: to pull
definition: To apply a force to (an object), in order that it moves towards the origin of the force that was applied.

name: punji
definition: Bamboo steak used as a trap on trails or around villages.

name: pus
definition: A whitish-yellow or yellow substance produced during inflammatory responses of the body that can be found in regions of pyogenic bacterial infections.

name: to push
definition: To apply a force to (an object), in order that it moves away from the origin of the force that was applied.

name: rabbit
definition: One of several small mammals of the family Leporidae, with long ears, long hind legs and a short, fluffy tail.

name: raft
definition: A collection of logs, planks, casks, etc., fastened together for floating on water.

name: rainbow
definition: A multicoloured arc in the sky caused by the refraction of light within droplets of rain in the air.

name: to be raw (uncooked)
definition: Of food, being either wholly or imcompletely cooked.
burmese: အစိမ်း၊ မပြုတ်

name: reed
definition: Any of various types of tall stiff grass-like plants growing together in groups near water.

name: to release (let go)
definition: To give freedom; to stop holding; to release from confinement or restraint.
burmese: လွှတ်ရန် သို့မဟုတ် လွှတ်ရန်

name: to remain (stay)
definition: To continue to be in the same place or state.
burmese: ဆက်လက်ရှိနေရန်

name: to remember
definition: To recall from memory.
burmese: မှတ်မိဖို့

name: to request (something)
definition: To ask for a service or physical goods, often without returning the favor in kind.
burmese: တိရစ္ဆာန်၏ခြေသည်း

name: rib (bone)
definition: One of the long curved bones which form the rib cage.

name: cooked rice
definition: Rice that has been prepared by boiling or steaming until it is soft and edible.

name: pounded rice
definition: A flour made from finely milled rice, distinct from rice starch which is produced by steeping rice in lye; rice powder.

name: sticky rice
definition: A type of rice grown mainly in Southeast and East Asia and the eastern parts of South Asia, which has opaque grains, very low amylose content, and is especially sticky when cooked. Also called oryza sativa var. glutinosa, sticky rice, sweet rice or waxy rice.

name: wild rice
definition: A plant of the genus Zizania with edible grains and stem.

name: unhusked rice (paddy)
definition: A flooded field in which rice is grown.

name: husked rice (uncooked)
definition: Rice that has not been boiled or otherwise prepared for eating.

name: rice husk
definition: The husk of rice seeds.

name: rice plant
definition: An erect grass, Oryza sativa, that grows in East Asia on wet ground and has drooping flower spikes and yellow oblong edible grains that become white when polished.

name: rice straw
definition: The dry stalks of the rice plant.

name: to ride
definition: To transport oneself by sitting on and directing an animal.

name: ring (on finger)
definition: A circular band, usually made of metal, that is worn on a finger as an ornament or symbol.
burmese: လက်စွပ်တစ်ကွင်း

name: to be ripe
definition: To be fully developed or mature, and ready to be eaten or used.

name: ritual (rite)
definition: A specific process or action used to practise religious or spiritual beliefs. This may be a ritual practiced at major events, before hunting, or at any other significant time.

name: river
definition: A stream of water which flows in a channel from high ground to low ground and ultimately to a lake or the sea, except in a desert area where it may dwindle away to nothing.

name: riverbank
definition: The land along the side of a river that is above the waterline.
burmese: မြစ်တစ်ကမ်း

name: rapids
definition: Fast flowing section of a stream, often shallow and with exposed rock or boulders.

name: to roast
definition: To expose to heat without adding fat or water until it is cooked, has a brown crust and becomes crispy.

name: to roll down
definition: To move something by turning it over and over, such as a log rolling down a hill.

name: to roll up (mat)
definition: To wrap something around itself, such as a mat or a piece of paper.
burmese: ဖျာကဲ့သို့ တစ်ခုခုကို လှိမ့်ရန်

name: roof (of building)
definition: The upper covering of a building or vehicle, typically supported by a framework.

name: root (tree)
definition: The absorbing and anchoring organ of a vascular plant; it bears neither leaves nor flowers and is usually subterranean.

name: rope
definition: Thick, strong string made of several strands that have been twisted together.

name: to be rotten
definition: Having changed its colour, smell or composition (partially or completely), due to being attacked and decomposed by microorganisms (relating to organic matter).

name: to be rough
definition: Having a texture that has much friction. Not smooth.
burmese: ကြမ်းတမ်းသည်

name: to be round
definition: Circular or having a circular cross-section in at least one direction.

name: to rub
definition: To move one's hand or an object over a surface or other object (maintaining constant contact and applying moderate pressure).

name: to rule (lead)
definition: To guide by moving in front.

name: ruler (chief)
definition: The person who has the highest authority in a group or organization.
burmese: အကြီးအကဲ သို့မဟုတ် အုပ်ချုပ်သူ
comment: CONCEPTICON has the measuring tool as the definition.

name: to be sacred
definition: To be regarded as holy or worthy of respect and devotion.

name: to be sad
definition: Feeling mentally uncomfortable because something is missing or wrong.
burmese: ဝမ်းနည်းစရာ

name: sago palm
definition: Common name for several plants which are used to produce a starchy food known as sago. // Predates rice as the staple food among some communities in western Arunachal Pradesh.

name: saliva
definition: The clear liquid that is secreted by glands in the mouth and is used to moisten food and aid in digestion.

name: salt
definition: A crystalline substance consisting of sodium and chlorine, used for seasoning or preserving food, or for a variety of other industrial and household purposes.

name: to be same
definition: Bearing full likeness by having precisely the same set of characteristics.
burmese: အတူတူဖြစ်ရမယ်။

name: sand
definition: A loose material consisting of small mineral particles, or rock and mineral particles, distinguishable by the naked eye; grains vary from almost spherical to angular, with a diameter range from 1/16 to 2 millimeters.

name: tree sap
definition: The juice of plants of any kind, especially the ascending and descending juices or circulating fluid essential to nutrition.

name: scab
definition: A bit of dried blood over a wound as part of the healing healing process.

name: scent (fragrance)
definition: A distinctive smell or aroma that can be detected by the nose.

name: to scrape (with edge)
definition: To move an object against another object such that abrasion or minor cutting occurs.
burmese: ခြစ်ရန် သို့မဟုတ် ခြစ်ရန်

name: to scratch (with nails)
definition: To rub or scrape (a part of the body) with a sharp object (e.g. to relieve an itching).
burmese: မကြေသေးသော ဆန်၊

name: scythe
definition: A farm tool consisting of a long bent blade attached to a shaft, that is designed for cutting straws of grass or grain from an upright position.
burmese: တံမြက်/တံစဉ်

name: sea
definition: A body of salt water that is smaller than an ocean and generally in proximity to a continent.
burmese: သမုဒ္ဒရာ၊ ပင်လယ်

name: dry season
definition: Yearly period of low rainfall in the tropics.

name: rainy season (monsoon)
definition: Period of year when most of a region's average annual rainfall occurs.

name: secluded place
definition: A private or isolated place away from others.
burmese: သီးသန့်နေရာ

name: section (segment)
definition: A segment or part of a larger whole.
burmese: အပိုင်း (ဥပမာ ဝါး)၊

name: to see
definition: To perceive with the eyes, or to comprehend mentally through observation or understanding.

name: seed
definition: A mature fertilized plant ovule, consisting of an embryo and its food store surrounded by a protective seed coat (testa).

name: to sell
definition: To provide goods or services in exchange for money.

name: to separate
definition: To cause something or someone to move away from something or someone else.
burmese: ခွဲခြားရန်

name: servant
definition: A person performing duties for others. For example a person employed in a household which cares about the domestic duties.

name: to settle (somwhere)
definition: To establish oneself in a new location and make it one's permanent home.
burmese: တစ်နေရာရာမှာ အခြေချဖို့

name: to sew
definition: To pass thread repeatedly through fabric or a material, using a needle, in order to join two or more parts or to make a pattern or motif.

name: shade (area)
definition: An area sheltered from direct sunlight, typically created by trees or other vegetation.

name: shadow (of something)
definition: Darkness, where light (particularly sunlight) is blocked.
burmese: မကျက်သောဆန်

name: to be shallow
definition: Having little depth, or being close to the surface of something.

name: to be sharp (of edge)
definition: Having a thin or narrow edge capable of cutting or slicing.
burmese: အစွန်းတစ်ခု၏ချွန်ထက်

name: to be sharp (of point)
definition: Having a fine point or edge that is able to cut or pierce.
burmese: ထက်မြက်သောအချက်၊

name: to shave (head)
definition: To remove hair from the skin by cutting it with a razor or other bladed implement.

name: shawl
definition: A rectangular piece of fabric worn over the shoulders or head, typically worn by men in Nagaland.

name: sheep
definition: A common, four-legged animal (Ovis) that is commonly kept by humans for its wool.

name: shield
definition: A device used to protect oneself or others from harm or danger when engaging in close combat. Typically woven from cane, carved from wood, or formed from toughened animal hide.

name: to shine (of sun)
definition: To emit light.
burmese: တောက်ပဖို့

name: to shiver
definition: To shake or tremble due to cold, fear, or excitement. To tremble.
burmese: တုန်လှုပ်ခြင်း။

name: to shoot (arrow)
definition: To fire a shot from a firearm, bow or other weapon.

name: to be short (duration)
definition: For a brief period or a short amount of time.

name: to be short (height)
definition: Small in length by comparison.

name: to be short (length)
definition: Small in length by comparison.
burmese: အတိုအရှည်ဖြစ်ရမည်။

name: to show (display)
definition: To make something visible to others.

name: shrimp
definition: Refers to some decapod crustaceans, although the exact animals covered can vary. Used broadly, it may cover any of the groups with elongated bodies and a primarily swimming mode of locomotion – chiefly Caridea and Dendrobranchiata.

name: to be shy
definition: To be hesitant or reserved in social situations, often due to timidity or lack of confidence. This is distinct from ashamed.

name: younger sibling
definition: Either sibling which is younger

name: side (of body)
definition: One of the two sides of the human or animal body, left or right, from the shoulder to the hip.
burmese: ခန္ဓာကိုယ်၏အခြမ်း

name: side (of something)
definition: The surface that is not the front or back of an object.
burmese: တစ်စုံတစ်ခု၏ဘက်

name: silver
definition: A very ductile malleable brilliant greyish-white element with symbol Ar and atomic number 47 having the highest electrical and thermal conductivity of any metal.

name: to be similar
definition: Having some particular qualities or characteristics in common, but not all of them.
burmese: အလားတူဖြစ်ရန်

name: to sing
definition: To produce musical sounds with one's voice, often in a rhythmic or melodic pattern.
burmese: သီချင်းသီဆိုရန်

name: to sink
definition: To go down in water, mud, quicksand etc. or to cause something to go down in it.
burmese: နစ်မြုပ်ရန်

name: elder sister
definition: The female sibling who is older than oneself.

name: younger sister
definition: The female sibling who is younger than oneself.

name: to sit
definition: To be in a position with the upper body upright and the legs resting.

name: to be skilled
definition: To possess a high level of ability or proficiency in a particular task or activity.
burmese: တစ်ခုခုကို ကျွမ်းကျင်ဖို့၊

name: skin
definition: The tissue forming the outer covering of the vertebrate body: it consists of two layers, the outermost of which may be covered with hair, scales, feathers, etc. It is mainly protective and sensory in function.

name: skirt (mekhela)
definition: An article of clothing, usually worn by women and girls, that hangs from the waist and covers the lower part of the body. // This should be specified as that worn by women, the mekhela, and not that of men, a loungyi.

name: skull
definition: The main bone of the head; the cranium.

name: sky
definition: The part of the earth's atmosphere and space outside it that is visible from earth's surface. During the day it is perceived as blue, and at night as black.

name: to sleep
definition: To rest in a state of decreased consciousness and reduced metabolism.

name: to be slippery
definition: Smooth or wet so that it is difficult to hold or stand on it.

name: to be slow
definition: With low speed.
japanese: ゆっくりと, おそい

name: to be small
definition: Having a small size or dimensions, often relative to others of its kind.
burmese: သေးငယ်ဖို့

name: to smell (intransitive)
definition: To give off a smell that can be perceived by the nose.
burmese: အနံ့ရှိရန်

name: to smell (something)
definition: To perceive the presence of molecules in the air by inhaling them through the nose.

name: to smell bad
definition: To emit an unpleasant odor or stench.

name: to smell good (fragrant)
definition: To emit a pleasant or desirable odor or fragrance.

name: to smile
definition: To make an upwards movement of the sides of the mouth, that indicates happiness or satisfaction.

name: smoke
definition: An aerosol, consisting of visible particles and gases, produced by the incomplete burning of carbon-based materials, such as wood and fossil fuels.

name: to smoke
definition: To inhale smoke from for example a cigarette or a cigar.
burmese: ဆေးလိပ်သောက်ရန်

name: to be smooth
definition: Not rough; having a surface texture that lacks friction.

name: snail
definition: (Gastropoda) Ventral footed mollusk, including land snails, terrestrial pulmonate gastropod mollusks.

name: snake
definition: Any reptile of the suborder Serpentes, typically having a scaly cylindrical limbless body, fused eyelids, and a jaw modified for swallowing large prey.

name: to sneeze
definition: To expel air rapidly as a reflex, usually induced by an irritation in the nose.

name: to snore
definition: To make a noise during sleep by vibration of soft respiratory tissues (soft palate, base of the tongue and pharyngeal walls), particularly during inhalation.

name: snot (liquid mucus)
definition: Mucus from the nose.

name: to be soft
definition: A state of consistency allowing alterations of form with ease, no big force required, to bring things into something of this state (such as e.g. soaked loam or clay soil).

name: some (portion)
definition: An unspecified quantity or number of.

name: son
definition: One's male child.

name: son in law
definition: The male marital partner of someone's child.

name: song
definition: A musical piece with lyrics (or words to sing); prose that one can sing.

name: soul, spirit (of living)
definition: In philosophical or religious belief the immaterial part of a human being.

name: to be sour
definition: Having an acid, sharp or tangy taste.
burmese: အချဉ်ဖြစ်ရန်

name: south
definition: One of the four major compass points, specifically 180°, directed toward the South Pole, and conventionally downwards on a map.

name: to sow (crops)
definition: To scatter or disperse seeds on a field.

name: soy bean
definition: The edible seed of the soybean plant which contains a lot of protein.

name: sparrow
definition: A small song bird, in the family Passeridae.

name: to speak
definition: To communicate by the use of words.
burmese: ပြောရန် သို့မဟုတ် ပြောရန်

name: spear
definition: a long, stabbing weapon for thrusting or throwing, consisting of a wooden shaft to which a sharp-pointed head, as of iron or steel, is attached.

name: to be special
definition: To be unique or different from what is ordinary or usual.
burmese: အထူးဖြစ်ရန်

name: spicy (of chilis)
definition: Provoking a burning sensation due to the presence of chillies or similar hot spices.
burmese: ငရုတ်သီးမှအစပ်

name: spider
definition: Any predatory silk-producing arachnid of the order Araneae, having four pairs of legs and a rounded unsegmented body consisting of abdomen and cephalothorax.

name: spiderweb
definition: A fine net of threads woven by a spider to catch insects.
burmese: ပင့်ကူအိမ်ကွန်ယက်

name: to spin (cotton)
definition: To twist or spin fibers of cotton into thread or yarn.

name: spirit (deity)
definition: A spiritual entity that is not as powerful as a deity.
burmese: စိတ်ဝိညာဉ်

name: to spit
definition: To forcefully evacuate saliva from the mouth.

name: splinter (injury)
definition: A small sharp piece of wood which is stuck in the skin.

name: to split
definition: To divide fully or partly along a more or less straight line.

name: to spoil (of food)
definition: Of food, to become bad, sour or rancid; to decay.

name: spoon (utensil)
definition: An implement for eating or serving, a small bowl with a long straight handle.

name: to spread (of roots)
definition: To spread out or open from a closed or folded state.
burmese: အမြစ်၏ပြန့်ပွားရန်

name: to squeeze
definition: To apply pressure to something from two or more sides at once.

name: flying squirrel
definition: A squirrel of the sub-family Pteromyinae of the family Sciuridae.

name: squirrel (general)
definition: A small or medium-sized rodent of the family Sciuridae.

name: to stand (in place)
definition: To assume an upright position on one's feet, often with the intention of remaining stationary for a period of time.

name: star
definition: A luminous celestial body that is made from gases (particularly hydrogen and helium) and forms the shape of a sphere.

name: shooting star
definition: Name for the visible path of a meteoroid.

name: to stay
definition: To live or remain in a particular place or location for an extended period of time.

name: to steal
definition: To take possession of property belonging to another without the consent of this owner; most typically when not observed, rather than by force.

name: to step
definition: To move the foot in walking; to advance or recede by raising and moving one of the feet to another resting place, or by moving both feet in succession.
burmese: ခြေတစ်လှမ်းယူရန်

name: to step on
definition: To place your foot on top of something, often accidentally or unintentionally.
burmese: တစ်ခုခုကို လှမ်းဖို့

name: stick (tree)
definition: A long, thin piece of wood, mainly left in the shape in which it grew, that does not bend.

name: to sting (of bee)
definition: To hurt, usually by introducing poison or a sharp point, or both.

name: stomach (organ)
definition: The organ of the digestive system responsible for breaking down food and extracting nutrients.

name: stone
definition: A hard, naturally occurring mineral material often used for building, sculpture, or paving.

name: to stop (moving)
definition: To halt one’s movement.
burmese: လှုပ်ရှားခြင်း သို့မဟုတ် တစ်ခုခုလုပ်ခြင်းကို ရပ်ရန်

name: storm
definition: An atmospheric disturbance involving perturbations of the prevailing pressure and wind fields on scales ranging from tornadoes to extratropical cyclones; also the associated weather and the like. (Source: MGH)
burmese: မုန်တိုင်း

name: to be straight
definition: Not crooked or bent; having a constant direction throughout its length.

name: stream
definition: A small river or large creek; a body of moving water confined by banks.

name: to be strong
definition: Capable of producing great physical force.

name: to suck
definition: To draw in a substance by creating a practical vacuum in the mouth, and as a result a difference in pressure.

name: sugarcane
definition: A tropical grass of the genus Saccharum having stout, fibrous, jointed stalks, the sap of which is a source of sugar.

name: sun
definition: The particular star at the centre of our solar system, from which the Earth gets light and heat.

name: sunshine
definition: Of the sun, to provide direct sunlight, or the warmth and light provided by the sun's rays.
burmese: နေရောင်ခြည်

name: to support
definition: To bear or carry the weight of someone or something.
burmese: ရုပ်ပိုင်းဆိုင်ရာထောက်ပံ့ရန်

name: surface (of liquid)
definition: The overside or up-side of a flat object such as a table, or of a liquid; the outside hull of a tangible object.
burmese: ရေမျက်နှာပြင်

name: surplus
definition: To have a large quantity or a lot of something, greater than ones needs.

name: swallow
definition: Any of the various passerine birds of the family Hirundinidae; martin.
burmese: swallow ဟုခေါ်သည်။

name: to swallow
definition: The reflex in the human body that makes something pass from the mouth to the pharynx and into the esophagus, with the shutting of the epiglottis.

name: to sway (in wind)
definition: To move or swing from side to side; or backward and forward; to rock.
burmese: သစ်ပင်ကဲ့သို့ ယိမ်းနွဲ့ရန်၊

name: to swear (oath)
definition: To declare or affirm solemnly and formally as true.

name: to sweat
definition: To excrete moisture from the skin through sweat glands, often as a result of physical exertion or high temperatures.

name: to sweep
definition: To clean a surface with a broom.

name: to be sweet
definition: Having the taste characteristic of sugar or honey.

name: to swell
definition: To become larger in size or volume, usually due to pressure or inflammation.
burmese: ဖောရောင်ရန်

name: to swim
definition: To move through the water, without touching the bottom.

name: table
definition: A piece of furniture that generally consists of a hard, flat, horizontal surface, which is elevated and stabilised by 3 or more legs (usually 4).

name: tail
definition: The appendage of an animal that is attached to its posterior and near the anus.

name: to take
definition: To seize or grasp something with one's hands, or to assume control or possession of something.

name: to be tall
definition: Having a large distance from the base to the top, often relative to other objects or structures.
burmese: အရပ်မြင့်သည်ဖြစ်စေ၊

name: tamarind (pod)
definition: A tropical fruit with a sour and slightly sweet taste.

name: taro (kochu)
definition: A starchy root vegetable commonly used in cooking. This should be distinguished from other starchy roots used as a foodstuff.

name: to taste
definition: To perceive the flavor of food or drink using the mouth and tongue.
burmese: မြည်းကြည့်ရန်

name: tattoo
definition: A marking made by inserting ink into the layers of skin to change the pigment permanently for decorative or other reasons.

name: tea (beverage)
definition: A hot drink made by infusing dried leaves of the tea plant in boiling water. This should be the general category of drinks and not marked for the specific preparation of the tea leaves. A native or near native term is expected for all languages in the region. .

name: to teach
definition: To impart knowledge or skill to someone through instruction.
burmese: သင်ကြားရန်

name: teacher
definition: A person who teaches, typically in a school but may also include any sort of instructor of mentor of skills or knowledge.

name: to tell
definition: To talk about a story giving its details; to give a detailed account of.

name: testicle
definition: The male sex gland that produces sperm and male hormones, found in some types of animals and humans.

name: to thank
definition: To express gratitude or appreciation. This will occasionally be a loan from a larger language, such as Burmese, as is the case in much of Tangsa-Nocte.
burmese: ကျေးဇူးတင်ရန်

name: that
definition: The basic distal demonstrative. Typically not marked for altitude, visibility, or emphasis, although superdistal/emphatic demonstratives may also occur and should be documented. Most languages in this area will distinguist primarily between proximal and distal, with a possible third option for emphasis.

name: that
definition: The emphatic/hyperdistal demonstrative.

name: to be thick (of liquid)
definition: Of liquid, having viscosity.

name: to be thick (of material)
definition: Relatively large distance from one surface to the opposite in its smallest solid dimension.

name: thief
definition: Someone who takes property belonging to someone else with the intention of keeping it or selling it.

name: to be thin (of material)
definition: Having a small distance from one surface to another, often relative to the object's size.

name: to be thin (people)
definition: Carrying little fat (of people).
burmese: ပိန်ဖို့၊ ပိန်တယ်။

name: to think
definition: Use ones mental power to form ideas or having used ones mental power to form ideas of conviction or belief.
burmese: စဉ်းစားရန်

name: to be thirsty
definition: To suffer from thirst; to have a craving to drink, which is often accompanied by the feeling of dryness in the mouth and throat.
burmese: ရေငတ်ဖို့၊

name: this
definition: Referring to the thing or things that are nearby or currently being discussed.

name: thorn
definition: A sharp, pointed projection on the stem or branch of a plant, developed as a form of defence from grazing animals.

name: thread (string)
definition: A long, thin and flexible form of material, generally with a round cross-section, used in sewing, weaving or in the construction of string.

name: to threaten
definition: To express the intention to harm or punish someone.
burmese: ခြိမ်းခြောက်ရန်

name: throat
definition: The passage in the neck as part of the digestive system through which food and air pass.
burmese: လည်ချောင်း

name: to throw
definition: To cause (an object) to move rapidly through the air, with the force of the hand or arm.

name: thunder
definition: The large booming sound in the sky during storms, as caused by lightning heating the air around it to a very high temperature, causing it to rapidly expand and contract.

name: to tie (general)
definition: To fasten or secure something by wrapping or looping a string, rope, or other material around it and knotting it.

name: tiger
definition: Panthera tigris. A large, carnivorous feline with distinctive orange and black stripes. This concept may be understood by speakers as any large cat belonging to the genus Panthera, so care must be taken to avoid ambiguity.

name: to be tight (of space)
definition: To be firm or constricting, lacking in space or room.
burmese: တင်းတင်းကျပ်ကျပ်ဖြစ်ရန်

name: time
definition: The dimension of the physical universe which, at a given place, orders the sequence of events.

name: tobacco pipe
definition: A device consisting of a mouthpiece, a long pipe stem and a pipe bowl, that is used to smoke tobacco.

name: today
definition: The present day, or the day that has recently occurred when uttered at night.

name: toe
definition: One of the extremities of the foot.

name: tomorrow
definition: The day after the present day.

name: fireplace tongs
definition: A tool consisting of two long arms with a pivot joint, used for gripping and lifting objects.

name: tongs (general)
definition: In need of some rest or sleep, due to lack of sleep or as a result of hard work or physical activity.

name: tongue
definition: The flexible muscular organ in the mouth that is used to move food around, for tasting and that is moved into various positions to modify the flow of air from the lungs in order to produce different sounds.

name: tonight
definition: The current or approaching evening or night.

name: tooth (general)
definition: A hard, calcareous structure present in the mouth of many vertebrate animals (including humans), generally used for eating.

name: torch
definition: A stick with a flame on one end used as a light source.

name: town
definition: A human settlement larger than a village but smaller than a city, typically located in a rural area.

name: tradition
definition: A long-established custom or belief that has been passed down from generation to generation.

name: to trample
definition: To tread heavily or forcefully on something or someone, resulting in damage to or flattening of the thing being treaded upon.

name: to trap
definition: To catch in a trap, to immobilize.

name: trap (snare)
definition: A device or enclosure designed to catch or restrain something or someone, typically used as a form of hunting. The form will differ depending on the animal for which it is meant. Multiple basic stems may occur for this concept based on such differences.
burmese: ထောင်ချောက်တစ်ခု

name: treasure (wealth)
definition: Valuable objects or money that have been hidden or lost and are subsequently sought after.

name: tree
definition: Any large woody perennial plant with a distinct trunk giving rise to branches or leaves at some distance from the ground.

name: treebark
definition: The protective outer layer of a tree trunk composed of dead cells, often used for medicinal or decorative purposes.
burmese: သစ်ပင်အခေါက်

name: branch
definition: A woody offshoot of a tree or shrub.

name: tribe (ethnic group)
definition: Group of people linked by the same linguistic and cultural traditions that usually live far from urban areas and practice their own legal rules and have their own political system.

name: trousers (pants)
definition: An item of clothing worn on the lower part of the body and covering both legs separately.
burmese: ဘောင်းဘီရှည်

name: to be true
definition: To be accurate or true.

name: turmeric
definition: Curcuma longa, a plant in the ginger family from which the rhizomes are harvested and used to create a deep yellow spice used to colour and flavour foods.

name: to turn around
definition: To rotate or move in the opposite direction in which one was previously facing or heading.
burmese: လှည့်ပတ်ရန်

name: to turn back
definition: To reverse direction and go back to a previous point.
burmese: ပြန်လှည့်ရန်

name: to turn over (overturn)
definition: To turn something upside down or completely over.

name: turtle (tortoise)
definition: A reptile of the order Testudines (the crown group of the superorder Chelonia), characterised by a special bony or cartilaginous shell developed from their ribs that acts as a shield.
burmese: လိပ် သို့မဟုတ် လိပ်

name: twig
definition: A small, thin branch or stem of a tree or bush.

name: to twist
definition: To wind several things around each other (e.g. in order to form a rope or thread).

name: umbrella
definition: A device used to protect against rain or sunlight, consisting of a canopy on a folding metal frame.

name: to be unripe
definition: Of a fruit or vegetable that has not yet fully developed.

name: to untie
definition: To loosen, as something interlaced or knotted; to disengage the parts of. To unbind, to free from restraint.

name: to urinate
definition: To pass urine from the body.

name: urine
definition: Liquid excrement consisting of water, salts and urea, which is made in the kidneys, stored in the bladder, then released through the urethra.

name: valley
definition: Any low-lying land bordered by higher ground; especially an elongate, relatively large, gently sloping depression of the Earth's surface, commonly situated between two mountains or between ranges of hills or mountains, and often containing a stream with an outlet.

name: vegetable
definition: Any of various herbaceous plants having parts that are used as food.
burmese: ဟင်းသီးဟင်းရွက်

name: venom
definition: A poisonous substance produced by animals, such as snakes or spiders.

name: very
definition: A hard protective outer layer that covers and protects the soft inner parts of an animal or plant.

name: village
definition: A small community of houses and other buildings, typically in a rural area, often organised under unified leadership and identifiable as a community.

name: vine (creeper)
definition: Any plant with a growth habit of trailing or climbing stems or runners. Alternatively, any type of lianas.
burmese: စပျစ်၊ တွား

name: to vomit
definition: To forcefully expel the contents of one's stomach through the mouth, often as a result of illness or the ingestion of harmful substances.

name: vulture
definition: A large bird of prey that feeds mainly on carrion or dead animals, and belonging to either the Gypaetinae or Aegypiinae subfamily of Accipitridae.

name: waist
definition: The part of the body between the ribs and hips, typically the narrowest part of the torso.

name: to wait
definition: To refrain from acting or moving for some duration or until some event occurs.
burmese: စောင့်ဆိုင်းရန်

name: to walk
definition: To move from one place to another by moving legs alternately, so that at least one foot is in contact with the floor or surface at any one time.
burmese: လမ်းလျှောက်ရန်

name: wall
definition: A structure built to enclose or divide an area, usually made of brick or stone, but potentially other materials as well. This should be distinct from a fence.

name: war
definition: A conflict or a state of hostility between two or more parties, nations or states, in which armed forces or military operations are used.

name: to be warm
definition: Having a temperature slightly higher than usual, still pleasant.

name: to bathe
definition: To clean oneself by immersion in water.
burmese: ရေချိုးရန်

name: to wash (general)
definition: To remove dirt and grime from an object, using water (usually with soap).
burmese: ဆေးကြောရန်

name: to wash clothes
definition: To clean pieces of clothing by using water and supplementary cleansing products as a part of hygiene routine.

name: to wash face
definition: To use water and clean one's face. This is often a distinct verb from other forms of wash.

name: wasp
definition: Any insect which is part of the superfamily Vespoidea of the order Hymenoptera. Distinct from bees and ants, the term may occur as a compound with the general bee morpheme. This will include hornets.

name: to watch
definition: To have one's eyes, one's attention on something or someone.
burmese: စောင့်ကြည့်ရန်

name: water
definition: Common liquid (H₂O) which forms rain, rivers, the sea, etc., and which makes up a large part of the bodies of organisms.

name: drinking water
definition: Water which is safe to drink, either from being from a spring or having been boiled or otherwise prepared in some way.

name: to wave
definition: To move one's hand or arm in a waving motion, with or without holding something like a flag.

name: to be weak
definition: To be lacking physical strength, or lacking strength or energy such as due to fatigue.

name: to wear (of clothes)
definition: Fix clothes on your body and carry them.

name: to weave (fabric)
definition: To create a fabric by interlacing threads.

name: weed
definition: A plant that grows wild and profusely, especially when considered undesirable for agriculture.

name: week
definition: a period of seven days

name: to weep (cry)
definition: To shed tears in response to an emotional state, such as sadness, pain, or happiness.

name: to be well lit
definition: Illuminated with a lot of light, shining brightly.
burmese: တောက်ပစွာလင်း

name: west
definition: One of the four principal compass points, specifically 270°, conventionally directed to the left on maps. The direction of the setting sun.

name: to be wet
definition: To be covered or soaked with water or other liquids.

name: to whistle
definition: To make a sound or a melody by forcing the breath out between closed lips.

name: whole (complete)
definition: Entire, not lacking anything.
burmese: အပြည့်အစုံ

name: to be wicked (cruel)
definition: Evil or morally wrong.

name: to ve wide (broad)
definition: Having a large distance from one side to another, often relative to the object's length or size.
burmese: ကျယ်သည်ဖြစ်စေ ကျယ်သည်

name: widow
definition: A woman whose spouse has died.

name: widower
definition: A man whose spouse has died.

name: wife
definition: The female partner in a marriage.

name: wind
definition: The natural movement of the air, especially in the form of a current blowing from a particular direction.

name: wing
definition: The appendage of a bird or insect used for flying or gliding, typically consisting of a thin, lightweight membrane stretched over a framework of bones or cartilage.

name: to winnow
definition: To separate the chaff from grain using wind or air.

name: winter (cold season)
definition: The coldest season of the year, between autumn and spring.
burmese: ဆောင်းရာသီ

name: to wipe
definition: To move an object or utensil over a surface or other object while maintaining contact, in order that a substance be removed from its surface.

name: to be wise
definition: Showing good judgement or the benefit of experience.
burmese: ပညာရှိဖြစ်ရန်

name: old woman
definition: A woman who is elderly, in the later years of the average lifespan or belonging to the oldest living generation.
burmese: မိန်းမကြီး

name: woman (female human)
definition: An adult human member of the sex that produces ova and bears young.

name: wood
definition: The substance making up the central part of the trunk and branches of a tree. Used as a material for construction, to manufacture various items, etc. or as fuel.

name: woodpecker (general)
definition: A bird with a strong bill and stiff tail feathers, that climbs tree trunks to find insects to eat through rhythmic pecking of the tree with its beak.

name: word
definition: A distinct unit of language (sounds in speech or written letters) with a particular meaning, composed of one or more morphemes, and also of one or more phonemes that determine its sound pattern.

name: to work
definition: To do an activity involving mental or physical effort, for the purpose of earning money or making a living in some way.
burmese: အလုပ်လုပ်ရန်

name: world (metaphysical)
definition: The Earth with all its inhabitants and all things upon it. Distinct from the planet itself (Earth) or the land underneath (ground).

name: worm (general)
definition: A generally tubular invertebrate of the annelid phylum.

name: to wrap (cloth)
definition: To cover or enclose something by folding or winding a material around it, such as in wrapping a child or wrapping a wound.
burmese: ထုပ်ပိုးရန်

name: wristband
definition: Decorative ornament on the wrist made of string, cloth or leather. Distinct from a bangle which is made of metal or other hard materials.

name: to yawn
definition: To open the mouth widely and take a long, deep breath because of tiredness or boredom.

name: year
definition: The time it takes the Earth to complete one revolution of the Sun (between 365.24 and 365.26 days depending on the point of reference).

name: last year
definition: The year before the current one.

name: next year
definition: The year after the current one.

name: this year
definition: The current year.

name: yeast
definition: Many species of unicellular fungi, most of which belong to the Ascomycetes and reproduce by budding. The genus Saccharomyces is used in brewing and winemaking because in low oxygen concentration it produces zymase, an enzyme system that breaks down sugars to alcohol and carbon dioxide. Saccharomyces is also used in bread-making. Some yeasts are used as a source of protein and of vitamins of the B group. (Source: ALL)

name: yesterday
definition: The day before today.
